		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001063_0001"/><!--pb/@n='65r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Hadley Green</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">14<hi rend="sup">th</hi> July 1857</p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I was totally 
<lb/>unable to <choice><sic>fulfill</sic><corr>fulfil</corr></choice>
<lb/>my intention of 
<lb/>calling on you 
<lb/>yesterday but 
<lb/>if you will 
<lb/>kindly send or 
<lb/>give the "copy" 
<lb/>I mentioned 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001063_0002"/><!--pb/@n='65v'--> 
<lb/>to <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Taylor</persName><placeName>1/ Robert 
<lb/>St Adelphi</placeName> he 
<lb/>will deliver it 
<lb/>safely. You had 
<lb/>better give him 
<lb/>the Medal too at 
<lb/>the same time. I shall 
<lb/>tell him to send 
<lb/>for it - he will 
<lb/>take care of it<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I would like a 
<lb/>woodcut of the 
<lb/>Balonda mode 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001063_0003"/><!--pb/@n='66r'--> 
<lb/>of carrying a chief 
<lb/>namely on the 
<lb/>shoulders. A lady 
<lb/>here who draws 
<lb/>well - the same 
<lb/>who did the head 
<lb/>dresses would 
<lb/>draw what I 
<lb/>want on a block 
<lb/>of wood if we 
<lb/>had it<reg>.</reg> It could then 
<lb/>be cut more speedily<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>If you could either 
<lb/>send one the size 
<lb/>of the musical instrument 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001063_0004"/><!--pb/@n='66v'--> 
<lb/>or tell <persName>M<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">r</hi></hi> Taylor</persName>
<lb/>where it could be had 
<lb/>we could soon put 
<lb/>the work in hand<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>I sent "Kane" with 
<lb/>3 pieces of M.S.S. 
<lb/>yesterday. Many 
<lb/>thanks for Kane<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c. </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>D. Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
